name: dineshsa****
body:
Fully Renovated & Furnished High Rise Floor 2-Bedroom Unit (Private Guarded Condominium) at M Centura Residence, Sentul City, Kuala Lumpur City.

Property Highlights:
• Unit Details:
• 2 Bedrooms, 1 Bathroom
• Size: 650 sqft
• High Floor with panoramic views of Genting Highlands and Batu Caves
• Total floors: 47 | Units per floor: 16
• Fully renovated & fully furnished:
• Full kitchen cabinet set
• Washing machine & refrigerator
• Air-conditioning in master bedroom
• Queen bed frame (without mattress)
• Water heater
• Curtains for all windows
- 4-seater sofa
• 65-inch TV with cabinet
• Study table with gaming chair
• Stand fan (backup unit)
• Option to provide Coway water dispenser upon request

Security & Safety:
• 24/7 security monitoring with CCTV, supervised by Polis Bantuan (Security Office at Ground Floor)
• Strict visitor registration system for enhanced safety (only authorized visitors allowed entry)
• Private rubbish room on every floor (cleaned and cleared daily)

Parking:
• 1 Private parking lot provided
• Additional parking slots available upon request through management (subject to availability) — RM120/month per extra slot
• Visitor parking available (covered)

Facilities:
• Grand drop-off lobby (Ground Floor)
• Mini Mart (open daily 8am - 12 midnight, Ground Floor)
• Parcel Room (24/7 secured with CCTV and guards, Ground Floor)
• Mail Room (Ground Floor)
• Friendly management office (Weekdays, office hours, Ground Floor)
• Olympic-size swimming pool (50 meters) with kids’ pool & jacuzzi (Level 10)
• Halal & Non-Halal BBQ Pit (Level 10)
• Floating Gym / Fitness Room (Level 10)
• Co-working & relaxation spaces (Level 10)
• Badminton Court (Level 10)
• Multi-purpose Hall (Level 10)
• Hammock Garden (Level 10)
• Car wash service (cash paid, Ground Floor)
• EV charging stations available at parking area

Accessibility & Nearby Amenities:
• Completed in January 2022 (Less than 3 years old)
• Total 1440 units (2 blocks) | Each block equipped with 8 guest lifts & 1 fire lift
• Covered RapidKL bus stop located right outside condo entrance
• Excellent connectivity to key locations (Google for verification):
• KLCC: 7 km (approx. 10 mins drive)
• KL Sentral: 9.5 km (approx. 15 mins drive)
• LRT Sentul Timur: 2 km (approx. 5 mins drive)
• KTM Sentul: 2 km (approx. 5 mins drive)
• Sentul Medical Center: 3.3 km (approx. 5 mins drive)
• Hospital Kuala Lumpur (GH): 3.8 km (approx. 6 mins drive)
• Sunway Putra Mall: 4.2 km (approx. 6 mins drive)
• 24/7 KK Mart & 7-Eleven within 1 km walking distance
- Medical Clinic 24/7 - within 100meters away walking distance
- ⁠Urban Market & 99 Speed Mart - within 100meters away walking distance
- ⁠Restoran Mamak 24/7 - within 100meters away walking distance
- ⁠Sentul Point Mall - 200meters away from Condominium (walking distance)

Access Cards Provided:
• 2 Master access cards for lift & guest parking
• 1 card for parking entrance

Rental Package:
• Monthly Rental: RM 1,900/month (Less than Market Price)
• 1-Year Tenancy Agreement (Minimum)
• 2 Months Security Deposit
• 1 Month Advance Rental
• Agreement & Legal Process Fee: RM 500
• Total Payment need to settle before signing the Tenant Agreement.

Other Terms & Conditions:
1. Tenant shall pay all utility bills (electricity, water, internet, etc.)
2. No subletting or short-term rental allowed without prior written consent.
3. Minor maintenance below RM 250 to be borne by the tenant.
4. Tenant shall maintain the property in good, clean, and tenantable condition.
5. Any damage beyond fair wear and tear will be deducted from the deposit.
6. Landlord reserves right to inspect the property with prior notice.
7. Renewal subject to mutual agreement at end of term.

Unit video will be shared to serious inquiries only.

NOTE: Serious inquiries onlu & NO AGENTS!

Direct Deal with Unit Owner:

staircase and less quiet.

name: Rey
body:
Pangsapuri Filantus Bandar Baru Bangi
Selangor - Bangi
==========
RM 1 200
(per month)
==========
Pangsapuri Filantus fully furnished berkonsep moden dan kemas pastinya sangat berbaloi kepada golongan pelajar atau keluarga kecil yang ingin kediaman sudah lengkap dengan barangan dekor yang cantik.

Rumah ini telah dihiaskan oleh jenama syarikat ID popular Projek MakeOver Interior Design bagi memberi keselesaan kepada anda yang ingin menyewa di kediaman ini.

KENAPA PILIH PREMIS INI:
1. Ruang dalaman rumah yang cantik, dihias lengkap dengan barangan rumah seperti gambar tersedia

2. Mempunyai 3 Bilik tidur lengkap dengan katil, tilam, cadar, bantal, karpet, ruang gantung pakaian, meja sisi dan lampu meja serta langsir

3. Bilik air x1 dan tandas x1 yang bersih serta mempunyai kekuatan air paip yang kuat dan puas untuk membersihkan diri dan barangan peribadi

4. Lokasi strategik di Teras Jernang Bandar Baru Bangi. Berdekatan dengan Universiti ternama seperti UKM, GMI Universiti, KPTM Bangi. Dekat dengan kawasan pusat bandar seperti Bandar Baru Bangi, Putrajaya, Cyberjaya, Kajang serta KLIA.

5. kediaman lengkap dengan dekor lengkap ruang tamu dan ruang makan, mempunya aircond 1.5hp di ruang tamu, barangan lengkap keperluan bilik tidur di semua bilik dan tandas, mempunyai rak terbuka serta peti sejuk di dapur kering, airfryer dan meja konkrit di dapur basah. Pili air juga mempunyai tekanan air yang kuat, sangat selesa menggunakan pili air.

6. Ada satu lot parkir kereta berbumbung untuk premis ini. Selain itu kawasan parkir terbuka juga banyak dengan syarat parkir dengan berhemah.


SANGAT SESUAI UNTUK ANDA YANG:
1. Pelajar yang ingin ruang privacy, tinggal dalam group kecil seperti 6 orang dan ingin kediaman yang lengkap dan cantik (Masuk bawa pakaian dah boleh terus diami)

2. Yang mempunyai keluarga kecil dan tidak mahu barang sarat dan ingin semua barang tersedia supaya senang nak plan suatu hari nanti dah ada kediaman sendiri

3. Yang ingin mendapatkan bilik secara privacy dan ingin mencari penyewa tambahan untuk sewakan bilik yang lain


Harga Promosi
RM1200/ bulan

BAYARAN PERTAMA UNTUK MASUK KE KEDIAMAN
RM1200 (Bulanan Pertama) + RM2400 (Deposit dua bulan) + RM1000 (Deposit Utiliti dua bulan)
= RM4600.00

* Ada kontrak penyewa dan pemilik kediaman
* Minimum tinggal adalah dua tahun, kurang maaf kami tidak ambil
* Untuk penyewa pembersih, boleh jaga barangan kediaman dan Muslim sahaja
* Tidak mahu penyewa bermasalah pembayaran. Cakap jelas-jelas dan awal-awal senang tak nak nanti isu di masa akan datang.

* Tertakluk terma dan syarat

Nestled in the heart of a vibrant, well‑connected neighborhood, this turnkey condominium offers an effortless blend of style, comfort, and convenience—ideal for growing families, professionals, or students. Fully furnished and thoughtfully appointed, the home features:

Spacious Living & Dining
Step into an open‑plan living area bathed in natural light from balcony entrance door. Plush sofas, a stylish coffee table that set the stage for relaxed evenings or lively gatherings, while the adjacent dining zone, complete with a sleek table for six, makes entertaining effortless.

Three Serene Bedrooms
Each bedroom is fully furnished with comfortable mattresses, closet, and ample storage:

Master Suite: Features a king‑size bed, sliding door wardrobe, make-up cabinet, and an ensuite bathroom.

Bedroom 2 & 3: Ideal for guests and children, these rooms each include a queen‑size bed, a bunk bed and built‑in wardrobes.

Two Modern Bathrooms
Both bathrooms are finished in neutral porcelain tile, with floating vanities, mirrors, and faucets. Perfect for winding down after a busy day.

Expansive Balcony
A private balcony that serves as a perfect spot for sipping your morning tea or enjoying an evening breeze.

Two Dedicated Car Parks
Forget the hassle of street parking—this unit includes two secure, covered carpark spaces, ensuring easy access and added peace of mind.

body:
Coastal Comfort Meets City Convenience – Fully Furnished 3-Bedroom Condo with Partial Seaview

Enjoy the best of both worlds in this beautifully presented 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom condominium—fully furnished and featuring a partial seaview that adds a refreshing coastal touch to your daily living. Perfectly suited for families, professionals, or students, this home combines practicality with peaceful charm in a sought-after location.

🌅 Partial Seaview
Wake up to calming sea breezes and unwind in the evenings with a view of the horizon —ideal for sipping coffee, working remotely, or enjoying a quiet sunset moment.

🛋️ Fully Furnished, Stylish Interior
Step into a tastefully furnished living space with comfortable seating, smart layout, and plenty of natural light. Every room is designed for comfort and convenience, making this a true turnkey home.

🍽️ Modern Kitchen Setup
The open-concept kitchen features ample cabinet space and modern appliances (fridge, stove, sink) for everyday meals or weekend entertaining.

🛏️ Three Cozy Bedrooms
Master Bedroom: A queen-sized bed, make-up closet, and ensuite bathroom with premium fittings.

Bedroom 2 & 3: Great for guests, kids, or a home office—each fully furnished and move-in ready.

🚿 Two Functional Bathrooms
Both bathrooms feature contemporary finishes, glass shower enclosures, and water heaters—designed for ease and comfort.

🚗 1 Dedicated Carpark
Includes a covered parking space, offering added convenience in this secure residential building.

name: Jerome Lim
body:
Stylish & Spacious – Fully Furnished 3-Bedroom Condo with Balcony

Welcome to your new home in the city—a fully furnished 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom condominium designed for modern living. With a smart layout, tasteful interiors, and a private balcony, this unit offers the perfect balance of comfort and convenience for families, young professionals, or students alike.

🏡 Comfortable, Move-In Ready Living
Step inside and instantly feel at home. The bright and airy open-plan living and dining area is fully furnished with a cozy sofa set, dining table, TV console, and elegant décor—perfect for both relaxing evenings and entertaining guests.

🍽️ Modern Kitchen
The well-equipped kitchen features ample storage, sleek countertops, and built-in appliances including a refrigerator, electric stove, and sink—ready for all your cooking needs.

🛏️ Three Cozy Bedrooms
Master Bedroom: Comes with a queen-sized bed, large wardrobe, and a private ensuite bathroom.

Bedroom 2 & 3: Ideal for children, guests, or a home office—each furnished with beds and storage.

🚿 Two Stylish Bathrooms
Both bathrooms are fitted with quality fixtures, including a curtain-enclosed shower, modern vanities, and water heaters for everyday comfort.

🌿 Private Balcony
Step out to your private balcony, the perfect spot for your morning coffee, a potted herb garden, or simply enjoying some fresh air after a long day.

🚗 1 Dedicated Carpark
Comes with a secure, covered carpark space for added peace of mind.

🏢 Facilities & Amenities
Enjoy access to a range of condo facilities:

Swimming pool & wading pool

Fully equipped gym

24-hour security & CCTV

Function room and landscaped gardens

Children’s play area

📍 Great Location
Strategically located with easy access to:

Public transport & major highways

Shopping malls, supermarkets, and eateries

Schools, medical centers, and lifestyle amenities

body:
Rumah untuk diSewa

Lokasi: Tepi Highway PLUS (Arah Utara)

*Rumah Banglo Setingkat - Taman Jelutong, Changlun*

~~~
*Kemudahan Rumah:*
• 4 bilik + 1 bilik utiliti , 3 bilik mandi
• 2 bilik tidur dengan katil queen & tilam + 1 extra tilam queen
• 1bilik tidur dengan katil single & tilam
• 1 peti sejuk
• 1 set meja makan
• Dapur gas 2 tungku atas kabinet
• langsir lengkap untuk semua tingkap & 2 sliding door
• Ruang kiri, kanan & belakang rumah yang luas
• Fully tiled + grill
• cermin fully tinted
• paip air luar
• kipas setiap bilik
• lampu boleh laras (terang/ sederhana/ malap)
- sesuai utk suasana santai atau tidur
• Rumah luas dengan halaman Dan ruang tanah di kiri,kanan & belakang rumah
• Rumah terletak di kawasan berbukit yang sejuk & privasi

*Kemudahan Berdekatan*

1. Surau Al- Ikhwan TJ
2. Taman permainan kanak- kanak
3.UUM (15 minit)
4. Unimap (arau). (15 minit)
5. Politeknik Pauh (15 minit)
6. CMart Changlun (5minit)
7. Kolej Matrikulasi Kedah, Changlun (3min)
8. MRSM Kubang Pasu (10 minit)
9. Sekolah Berasrama Penuh Integrasi Kubang Pasu (SBPI) (13 minit)
10. Pekan Napoh (5 minit)

🪻Kriteria Penyewa:

• Seorang yang pembersih, amanah, dan bertanggungjawab

• Komitmen bayaran sewa yang baik

• Mempunyai kerjaya tetap atau pelajar pascasiswazah (Master/PhD) yang serius dan mahukan suasana rumah yang selesa & tenang. (Sesuai untuk tinggal bersama kawan sepenyambungan pengajian (max 3–4 orang)

- No Couple

body:
Stylish & Spacious – Fully Furnished 3-Bedroom Condo with Balcony

Welcome to your new home in the city—a fully furnished 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom condominium designed for modern living. With a smart layout, tasteful interiors, and a private balcony, this unit offers the perfect balance of comfort and convenience for families, young professionals, or students alike.

🏡 Comfortable, Move-In Ready Living
Step inside and instantly feel at home. The bright and airy open-plan living and dining area is fully furnished with a cozy sofa set, dining table, TV console, and elegant décor—perfect for both relaxing evenings and entertaining guests.

🍽️ Modern Kitchen
The well-equipped kitchen features ample storage, sleek countertops, and built-in appliances including a refrigerator, electric stove, and sink—ready for all your cooking needs.

🛏️ Three Cozy Bedrooms
Master Bedroom: Comes with a queen-sized bed, large wardrobe, and a private ensuite bathroom.

Bedroom 2 & 3: Ideal for children, guests, or a home office—each furnished with beds and storage.

🚿 Two Stylish Bathrooms
Both bathrooms are fitted with quality fixtures, including a curtain-enclosed shower, modern vanities, and water heaters for everyday comfort.

🌿 Private Balcony
Step out to your private balcony, the perfect spot for your morning coffee, a potted herb garden, or simply enjoying some fresh air after a long day.

🚗 1 Dedicated Carpark
Comes with a secure, covered carpark space for added peace of mind.

Swimming pool & wading pool

Fully equipped gym

24-hour security & CCTV

Function room and landscaped gardens

Children’s play area

📍 Great Location
Strategically located with easy access to:

Public transport & major highways

Shopping malls, supermarkets, and eateries

Schools, medical centers, and lifestyle amenities

Casa Indah 2 is a beautifully designed and a unique leasehold development located in Persiaran Surian, Kota Damansara, Selangor near Petaling Jaya. The construction of this project was done by a famous development company known as the Damansara Impian which is a subsidiary company of the Dijaya Group Corporation. The development of this project was completed in the year 2008. It is considered to be a great addition in the Selangor property. The property is going to boom in the future, making it ideal from an investment perspective.

Casa Indah 2 is indeed a great place to live in. The development offers many great facilities and features that the residents of many new developments only dream of having. The residents of the development can enjoy a beautiful nursery in the development and enjoy some fresh environment in the development. There is a mini market in the development from where the residents can spend some unforgettable time with their family and friends. Multipurpose hall is also available in the development which can be used on different occasions by the residents. The development company did not forget about the children and has developed a lovely children’s playground in the area where the children can enjoy while remaining in the development and without worrying the parents.

Casa Indah 2 was developed strategically keeping in mind the importance of accessibility of the location. The residents do not have to worry about moving to and from the location even if they do not have their own vehicles. The development is easily accessible via LDP, NKVE and Penchala Link. Public transportation is also available in the area and the residents of the development can use the Taman Paramount LRT Station, Taman Bahagia LRT Station and Kelana Jaya LRT Station to move to any place in the city. Furthermore, taxis and buses to move to and from the location easily. Other than its strategic location, the area is surrounded with plenty of amenities. The residents do not have to worry about anything in the area because everything is easily available in the locality. Educational institutions such as Honsbridge Academy, Smart Reader Kids, Little Kingdom and SEGi University College are just a short distance away from the development. There are many shopping spots as well near the development and few of the famous shopping spots near the development are namely Sunway Giza Mall, 7-Eleven and Pasar Segar Fresh Eden from where the residents can shop for almost anything they want. Furthermore, there are many eateries, mosques, petrol stations, churches and hospitals as well in the area, making sure that the residents of the development do not have to worry about anything.

Casa Indah 2 provides other facilities and features as well, such as a swimming pool and a great gymnasium equipped with latest exercising machines where the residents can work out while remaining in the development and enjoy a healthy lifestyle. The development also provides complete parking facility for its residents. Most importantly, the development is equipped with modern security gadgets and provides 24 hour security to its residents to make sure that the residents are protected from any kind of external threats while they are in the development.
